title: OFT Inc Recalls Beef Products Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, June 15, 2015 OFT, Inc, a Henderson, Nev., establishment, operating as Whakyung Foods, Inc., is recalling approximately 67,232 pounds of commercial-use beef leg bone extract and beef concentrate products produced in Australia and New Zealand that were not presented at the U.S. point of...
